message: "If you use this public checkpoint, cite the Zenodo record DOI or the stable concept DOI."
title: "Deep Origin Theory — J2C Result Release V1: Canonical J2R Rerun and Coefficient-Only Total-Scaling No-Go"
type: report
authors:
  - family-names: "Alhulays"
    given-names: "Osama"
    affiliation: "Independent Researcher"
